FDP’s Koch-Mehrin Must Answer Plagiarism Accusations, SZ Says

-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 
2011-05-11T05:52:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-11/fdp-s-koch-mehrin-must-answer-plagiarism-accusations-sz-says.html
Silvana-Koch Mehrin, a German Free
Democrat lawmaker who sits in the European Parliament, is to be
asked to defend herself against charges of plagiarism in her
doctoral dissertation, the Sueddeutsche Zeitung reported.  The charges are serious enough for Heidelberg University to
consider revoking Koch-Mehrin’s doctorate if she doesn’t provide
an adequate explanation, the newspaper reported, without saying
where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt 
 jblack25@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  